026 * <h5 class='figure'>Schema</h5>

028 *    atomSource =

030 *          atomCommonAttributes,
031 *          (atomAuthor*
032 *          &amp; atomCategory*
033 *          &amp; atomContributor*
034 *          &amp; atomGenerator?
035 *          &amp; atomIcon?
036 *          &amp; atomId?
037 *          &amp; atomLink*
038 *          &amp; atomLogo?
039 *          &amp; atomRights?
040 *          &amp; atomSubtitle?
041 *          &amp; atomTitle?
042 *          &amp; atomUpdated?
043 *          &amp; extensionElement*)
044 *       }
045 * </p>
046 *
047 * <h5 class='section'>See Also:</h5><ul>
